#

Citrus Burst Smoothie

5 min
$3.5
220 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeHigh Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Beverage

Tags:

SmoothieHealthyQuick

Description

A refreshing and energizing smoothie bursting with the zesty flavor of oranges, perfect for a quick breakfast or snack.

Ingredients

  • fresh orange juice: 1 cup
  • banana: 1 ripe
  • greek yogurt: 1/2 cup
  • honey: 1 tablespoon
  • ice cubes: 1 cup
  • chia seeds: 1 tablespoon
